spirit:component.spirit:description: The DPU is designed to accelerate the computing workloads of deep learning inference algorithms widely adopted in various computer vision applications, such as image/video classification, semantic segmentation, object detection/tracking. An efficient tensor-level instruction set is designed to support popular convolutional neural networks, such as VGG, ResNet, GoogLeNet, YOLO, SSD, and MobileNet, among others. The DPU is scalable to fit various Xilinx Zynq/MPSoC devices from edge to cloud to meet many diverse applications’ requirements.
